messages.message: Not sure if this is a known issue. On PreProd, in Build, when I select object detection for the project, it doesnt matter whether I select single field or table: it is always a table. Also, if I started off without object detection, got a single field, then say switch to table (at which point the document goes through object detection), the output becomes a table. But I'm not able to ever change it back. It stays a table regardless of the fact I change it to Single Field and re-run it. It will always be a table.
